data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to Casa Futura! This property is within the Sunset Park neighborhood. It is a sprawling oversized corner lot making this a truly enchanting place to build your future house to call home. The possibilities are endless, with ample space to create your own indoor/outdoor oasis or expand upon the existing features or even construct a brand new abode. A chance to create your dream home without the burden of unattainable prices. The current dwelling boasts a split floor plan, anchored by a capacious family room with a wood-burning fireplace . As you'll discover the current home has insulated windows, new HVAC system, resurfaced pool with brick pavers. Location Location: This community offers an exceptional school district, adding to the desirability.  The location is convenient to the best shopping and restaurants Tampa has to offer. Minutes away from the water, several marinas, various athletic/recreation facilities make it easy for the whole family to have fun year-round.  Note Pictures are not current
